OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, but some drier spells
OL,7,Fof weather too. Strong southwesterly
OL,8,Fwinds at first will ease by the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with chance of some
OL,12,Flight rain to start, but soon becoming
OL,13,Fdry and largely clear through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FIt will stay dry with good
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells through Friday.
OL,18,FLight winds through the day will
OL,19,Ffreshen somewhat in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
