OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith some bright spells Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning, cloudier with some rain
OL,8,Flater, strong southwesterly winds
OL,9,Facross Shetland. Variable cloud and
OL,10,Fmainly dry Sunday and Monday with the
OL,11,Fodd shower.
